item.title: Luis Rodriguez
item.author: team@silocitylabs.com (Silo City Labs LLC)
item.description: About As a self-employed software developer right out of school, I developed websites for other businesses, I created content management systems in English and Spanish of which I am both fluent in. Also developed a framework for multiple software projects. Although I only have an Associate’s Degree I don’t feel that it limits my ability to create great programs and websites.
